snippet.title: A Small Car 2
snippet.description:
A Small Car is back!

A Small Car 2 is a 3D racing game made with Flare3D and Flash. Drive through 12 levels as fast as possible. Earn stars to unlock other cars and a bonus level. Stay on the road!

This game was made by A Small game.

http://www.asmallgame.com
